Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.95,0:00:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A non-integrist person wouldn't be worried about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.93,0:01:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of integrity that you worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of spiritual responsibility, you worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.32,0:01:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A person of low integrity wouldn't even be concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,about the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But, like yourself, I tended to be scrupulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.74,0:01:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I tended to scrupulosity and perfectionism, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.62,0:01:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Agonized everything, whether it was, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.21,0:01:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in today's language, you're above or below 200, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.52,0:01:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is also about karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.90,0:01:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My understanding is that you have said that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,animals and people calibrating below 200
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,do not have individual karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.62,0:01:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't say individual karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.62,0:01:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have an awareness of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:01:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But they don't realize that that experience
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.19,0:02:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming out of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.27,0:02:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So they cannot extrapolate that to other human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.97,0:02:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,See, over 500, I mean, you know, over 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you say, yeah, but how is that gonna affect others
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,if I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.69,0:02:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Below 200, you don't care how that affects others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.39,0:02:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's their problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.79,0:02:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But over 200, no, you take on spiritual responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know what you got that from,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.14,0:02:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,when I said that you don't develop an etheric body,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,etheric brain, until over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's true, you don't have an etheric.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, the karma of people below 200 is group karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's group karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, from 200 up, you got individual responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Up to that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you're like one of the mob.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So by agreement, let's say a mob in front of the guillotine,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,they're all getting there with their netting,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,get there early.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They love to watch the heads get chopped off, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They have formed a group karmic energy field, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So they're subject to the karma of that animal level.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.09,0:03:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The cat is subject to the consequence
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,of the karmic energy field of cat-ness, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,With the exception of the cat's purr
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and the dog's wagging tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know when we've asked about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.56,0:03:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,we said we weren't allowed to ask about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Something unique about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But so, up to 200, you inherit the group karma,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the karma of that group, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And then from 200 on, it gets individual,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,let's ask that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.62,0:03:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a fact, the Lord resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It was surprising when we came across it to tell you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pick it up faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.07,0:04:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,consequences of group karma in massive planetary things. How come just they
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,were underneath the volcano as it erupted? Everybody knows this thing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,erupts periodically, and yet they're living there. Why is that? Then they all
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,get killed by the volcano. I mean, so obviously a group karmic participation,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is it not? Yeah. See, there's also the upside to the group karma, see? Not just
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the downside, but because they experience love of each other in that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,village and attachment to home and the valuation of love and it's various
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,expressions. So, there's not just downside, you know, but also upside. Must be something to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,love your village so much that you just hang out there even though it's going to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,get buried under a volcano, you know? Just can't leave home, I don't know. I understand them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a question about choice, and I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,very curious about the relationship between the two. You know, it's a lot of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,About choice, I'm not really sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.33,0:05:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,After listening to some of the things you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you said that lots of times you'll have thoughts will come up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.11,0:05:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and your ego will take credit for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do I know when I'm choosing and when my egos,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,you said that lots of times thoughts come out of nothingness as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but we have free will and choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.35,0:05:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do I tell the difference between the two?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what's coming up are options.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming out of a nothingness into a manifestation as thinking this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And they tend to create options continuously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, should I have a sip of coffee now or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Or should I stop and do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I let the coffee wait to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Will he feel offended if I stop and have coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So like multiple options are existing simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The propensity is going to depend on your level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Which of the choices are going to seem to be the most attractive, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And certain options are going to be zeroed out,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,not even an option because of who you've become, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's a variety of options and I can choose a multiple number of those options at any time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Or does the field determine what I'm going to choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The field is where it's presented, you might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you perceive within that field what looked to you to be the,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, the various options.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.96,0:06:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you don't have a choice about whether you're going to make a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have a choice about making a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to make a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When your foot's in the air, you've got to put it down somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't stand for 20 years with this foot trying to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the mind works so quickly, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So the propensity, so what you're seeing is the consciousness level
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,brings up propensities and options that would not come at a different level.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so then I would be, then I do influence things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's not the same as cause, but it's influenced because it's a part of the...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, who you are is the field now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's influencing the options that have seemed to you, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you could say, I could let him die or not let him die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, at a certain level, you can't let him die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,At another level, you've got to let him die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's correct depends on the contextualization of that level.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:07:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,At a certain level, it's wrong to let him die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Another level, it's wrong to let him live.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,See what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It all depends on context.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.99,0:08:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've quoted to this group the guilt I had for a great deal of time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that after goring a guy right in the groin with a spear,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not administer the coup de grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a mistake to let him live.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There, I should have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,One warrior's obligation to the other brought his suffering to an end,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,like you leave one bullet in a revolver, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, then it would depend on context.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I had to go through it in this lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and I recall the exact failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a moral failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My obligation is one warrior to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You give him an easy way out of this pain and suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it depends on where you're at at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:08:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I was learning then, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, is that the influence of that situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that's not the same as causing it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.66,0:09:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not causal, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But what's unresolved gets brought back to choose again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A Course in Miracles presents that nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's even called choose again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're represented, now choose again, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If that happened with that warrior again,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I would, of course, administer the coup de grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say to him, okay, and he'd say okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So, see how it differs then depending on the context.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for asking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ten to four.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.52,0:09:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make the answer shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we started earlier so I could go on and on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't go on and on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to be brief and short to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been bad again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,First, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I flew here with my friend from London yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to come and be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And 20 years ago when I started on my kind of conscious path
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.63,0:10:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,of development through being sentenced through the course
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,to Alcoholics Anonymous and then that kind of started
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,this whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And about every five years in my personal obsession
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,with my enlightenment, my whole life seems to fall apart
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I'm not who I think I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.82,0:10:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And about a year and a half ago I started reading your material
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and listening to your tapes and then it really fell apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, my business went, my wife went,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:11:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the house went, the car went, the children's private schools went,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, everything went.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I'm living in a tiny little rented flat in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.86,0:11:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just outside of London.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've never had less in terms of, you know, having a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is when I force myself to make my career work,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When I surrender myself more and more, I usually end up with less and less.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, like I want to provide for my children
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and my business is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be able to provide for my ex-wife and I've got no work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know if I go out there and just, you know, give it some stick
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and forget about surrendering everything, I can make things happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't want to work like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I do want to be able to continue to surrender myself to God,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to the God of my understanding and be able to provide for my children.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:12:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're saying is that they're alternate whereas actually they do work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You can continuously be a provider and also constantly surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that you're going to be presented with different things to surrender
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,than you would have been if you had not participated back in the workaday world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, if you live your life in a contemplative style,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to leave the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can still participate in the world, at least up to a certain level.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So I would try that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Try participating in the world to fulfill that other obligation
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and continue the spiritual work as a continuous contemplation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you one more thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I can drive a cab and also be contemplative.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you one more thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The more I try and solve my money problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the worse it tends to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:12:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything I do is to be able to make more money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I surrender to make more money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I go out and knock on doors to get business to make more money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm in this kind of paradox of wanting to give all that up,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but I want to give it all up so I'll have more of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can provide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just don't know if I'm missing the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.16,0:13:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a job, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind working.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I would just get a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just get a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget the business, business.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget the what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Business.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just get a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.82,0:13:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the Buddha said in my ear, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. David.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My question has to do, I know you came in this incarnation with a very honed intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is, you seem to be sharing with us some divine wisdom and knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm just curious how that comes to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.86,0:14:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What was becomes replaced by a different state.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This state is complete and total within itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This state is unmoving, non-responsive, has no volition, couldn't care less whether you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,learn anything, whether I'm a teacher or not, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.92,0:14:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:15:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, that presence within responds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It uses the intellect as a tool, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.85,0:15:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But actually, there's nobody there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy activates.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It activates the apparatus appropriately, depending on who's approaching about what,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,see?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And that precipitates back an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no knowingness what's going to be said until I've just heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.60,0:15:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no, like, think of an answer and then say the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,See, that's coming from causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It just is of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's hard to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the mind thinks in cause and effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinks there must be a causal agent, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That does this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't a this that does that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It is, it radiates out of that which it is, spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:16:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, basically...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called the Purusha in Sanskrit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.55,0:16:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're dying to know the term, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, your job was to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,To...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You came in as a teacher and then you reached that level where you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.99,0:16:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're open to the teachings being channeled through you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get any channeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Channeling is dualistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a that channeling a this to a this, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a consequence of that which you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the radiance of beauty?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The flower is not doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The flower is that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't come into this world to be beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're projecting an intentuality which is a dualistic conceptualization.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It radiates what it smells like because of that which it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.86,0:16:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.86,0:17:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's easy, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, you are expressing your teacher-ness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the world would call it, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.14,0:17:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, each of us has something we came to express.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is also a teacher to those who are behind you because we're all on an evolutionary
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,scale of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, compared to this one, you're a student, but compared to this one, you're a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, probably the preponderance of humankind calibrates lower than you do, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, to them, you radiated an energy which uplifts and sustains them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, each one is a student of that which is ahead and a teacher to that which is behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.13,0:17:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we are all either a teacher or a student depending on the relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm with somebody and he's a better carpenter than I am, then I'm the student and he's the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,teacher, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:17:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.10,0:18:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to know if it's in my highest good to leave my marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.78,0:18:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a complicated one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.85,0:18:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'd have to pray for guidance and handle it the best you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that for you because I'd be robbing you of the karmic consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What I get is that it's a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's an important decision because what you're going to do is going to depend on your
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,values and how you prioritize those values, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:19:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be robbing you of the karmic benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be making a judgment call.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.76,0:19:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a tough one for everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My desire is to surrender to God everything but peace and love, which I've learned from
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would like to know how best I am to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's by your overall alignment and commitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, you do it by prayer and by service and asking God's will in all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day in the 12-step groups, you take a moral inventory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And you ask for God's guidance and his will for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.69,0:20:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I best be of service to thee, O Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And then that invocation, you put out with great devotional intensity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And then your life becomes somewhat...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What you've just done by virtue of the Heisenberg principle is you've just changed the options
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that are going to be coming up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,See, this was going to be coming up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.41,0:20:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,With that invocation, this comes up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.41,0:20:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you've just changed the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the spiritual intention is already working in people's lives, and they don't recognize
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it, so they think that they're failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's in front of you right now is the consequence of what you've been asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not being able to see, not having any money, all those things are the consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:20:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.46,0:21:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.67,0:21:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, for years I led a prayer group, and then I hit a point where I was not sure if I should
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Should pray?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Not...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.04,0:21:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as a group.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,To lead a group.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.04,0:21:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,To lead a group in a healing ministry kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.04,0:21:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Lead a prayer group.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess that sort of is my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a value in praying together as a group for people that request it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.23,0:21:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, as I said here, the intention of the student, the intention of the teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and the intention of the group, the three together form a very powerful field.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.23,0:21:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So when people group together in prayer, a prayer group is a very positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:21:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, silent unity, for instance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.23,0:22:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.23,0:22:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Miracles happen all the time out of silent unity.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.23,0:22:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.90,0:22:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.45,0:22:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.45,0:22:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.48,0:22:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, could you talk about some of the differences between a student and a prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.48,0:22:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,group?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.48,0:22:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.48,0:22:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A state that might be psychologically destabilizing and one that might be spiritually
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.48,0:22:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,growthful?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.48,0:22:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You may not be able to tell the difference, because sometimes spiritual growth seems to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.90,0:22:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,manifest as a psychological disorder temporarily, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.74,0:22:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Because all your values and your paradigm of reality may shift, see?
