Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.80,0:34:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Other than beta blockers,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.52,0:34:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.43,0:34:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Some physical conditions you've got to
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.75,0:34:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,just live with.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.54,0:34:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was born myopic and nearsighted
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.98,0:34:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and couldn't see well besides.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.58,0:34:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.80,0:34:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Pretend like you like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.84,0:35:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What else can you do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.58,0:35:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.24,0:35:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretend like you like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.04,0:35:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.20,0:35:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.32,0:35:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.60,0:35:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.34,0:35:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.60,0:35:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope this question is appropriate
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.78,0:35:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,because I know you've been talking a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.12,0:35:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,about the illusory nature of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.79,0:35:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not illusory, but it leads to illusion, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.19,0:35:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego is very much there, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.83,0:35:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,As a former mental health practitioner,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.74,0:35:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,could you say something about the,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.98,0:35:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the limits or potential of hypnosis
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.98,0:35:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and self-hypnosis about changing
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.36,0:35:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,a person's subconscious negative beliefs
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.56,0:35:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,about himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.88,0:36:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, if used within the correct context,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.16,0:36:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's a useful tool, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.40,0:36:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Depends on what your intention is.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.80,0:36:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're looking for a magical cure
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.00,0:36:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,or something, I don't think that's
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.74,0:36:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the proper use, but you could use
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.54,0:36:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,hypnosis to get to the roots of it
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.00,0:36:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,so that you see what the roots
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.52,0:36:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,of the problem are.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.96,0:36:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe go on a path, you could do a past lifetime, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.56,0:36:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,to see maybe its historical origin.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.48,0:36:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I would use it for clarification rather than
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.64,0:36:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to sort of magically cure something
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.00,0:36:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and accomplish something.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.18,0:36:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I would use it for deeper inner insight.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.87,0:36:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think it's a useful tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.06,0:36:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, with that, then what would you say would be
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.82,0:36:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the best tool for someone to fix self-esteem?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.41,0:36:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,To fix self-esteem?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.47,0:36:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, self-esteem isn't just a thing, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.89,0:36:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a component.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.29,0:36:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just pause it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.52,0:36:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the overall level of the ocean, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.52,0:36:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just change the level of the ocean, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.52,0:37:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-esteem, first of all, is a judgment, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.01,0:37:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But no, in every case, it's rather complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.63,0:37:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's valuable to you because it drives you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.33,0:37:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,within to understand yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.27,0:37:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll arrive at the answer yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.77,0:37:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll arrive at the answer yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.94,0:37:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be some self-condemnation
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.02,0:37:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.28,0:37:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You've forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.55,0:37:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be somebody programmed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.44,0:37:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to cancel that program.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.28,0:37:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,See, one's esteem should not be a matter of
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.00,0:37:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,come see, come saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.59,0:37:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a gone conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.55,0:37:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a done.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.35,0:37:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a done.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.19,0:37:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a matter to be questioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.94,0:37:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Your value or your worth is not a matter of question.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.79,0:37:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Your existence already answers whether you're worth anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.78,0:37:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,God created you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.64,0:37:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what more do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.64,0:37:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You came from Wal-Mart, so I mean, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.12,0:38:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.86,0:38:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.42,0:38:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Life via God, body by Wal-Mart, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.00,0:38:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,General Motors.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.86,0:38:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Body by General Motors.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.50,0:38:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.10,0:38:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Life by God, body by Wal-Mart?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.94,0:38:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.18,0:38:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, self-worth, you're denying the divinity of your own essence,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.92,0:38:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,your creation, you know, which is created of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.91,0:38:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You can hardly ask, what is this worth, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.31,0:38:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.81,0:38:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My question to you is, what is this worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.69,0:38:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To you is surrendering everything to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.64,0:38:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I say, and this too, Lord, I often go, well, maybe I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.63,0:38:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You winced, you winced, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.03,0:38:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And all my money too, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.36,0:38:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I surrendered my youth and good luck, and you see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.46,0:38:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And with children as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.80,0:38:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.22,0:38:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that they're, like, I know that they're in the hands of the Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.68,0:39:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but then just to let them go, you know, as they get older.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.41,0:39:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.33,0:39:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand that, but just to do it without guilt of being, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.34,0:39:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, just...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.20,0:39:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so it brings up stuff a lot with a kid, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.64,0:39:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's attachment, there's control.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.64,0:39:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only to relinquish them to live their own life,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.34,0:39:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but to fulfill their own karma, see, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.00,0:39:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.42,0:39:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's being a good parent, of course, is sooner or later you've got to let them go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.98,0:39:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as a linear control...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.08,0:39:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.38,0:39:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But not as far as the contextualization of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.98,0:39:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,which is beyond distance and presence and physicality.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.50,0:39:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So the love you have for them, they've already incorporated.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.58,0:39:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They better...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.77,0:39:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the love that you give to the child in and of itself is worthless
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.13,0:39:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,unless the child incorporates it in their own self-concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.66,0:40:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The child who's been deprived of love in early childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.42,0:40:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,hasn't incorporated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.09,0:40:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The good, loving parent can't really experience themself
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.33,0:40:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,as loving or lovable or worthwhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.90,0:40:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be they've already picked up that energy from you
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.92,0:40:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and they don't need it anymore in a direct fashion, one-to-one fashion,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.50,0:40:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,because they've already adopted that principle, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.30,0:40:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But for me to let that go, like, I know my children know how to love
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.80,0:40:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and that I have been a loving parent,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.10,0:40:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but then as they go...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.60,0:40:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,through their life, and not to worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.49,0:40:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, not to worry?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.49,0:40:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, something might happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.49,0:40:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way you can not worry is to be dead, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.55,0:40:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The infant's worried the minute it's born.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.58,0:41:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It begins crying and bawling and mewling.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.58,0:41:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The mother's worried the minute it's born.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.58,0:41:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The nurses are worried. The doctor's worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.58,0:41:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The neighbors are worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.58,0:41:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to not worry? Yeah, God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.78,0:41:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't worry hard enough. That's your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.38,0:41:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.60,0:41:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And I bring all the love and blessings of every member
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.73,0:41:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Dr. Hawkins Study Group in Albuquerque
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.73,0:41:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and in Santa Fe.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.73,0:41:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.73,0:41:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.73,0:41:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a religious science practitioner,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.73,0:41:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and since studying with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.73,0:41:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come into a great deal of conflict
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.73,0:41:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,about the method of prayer that is used in religious science.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.73,0:41:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a lot of people come to me
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.73,0:42:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and ask me to pray for them, you know, for specific things.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.73,0:42:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And the whole idea behind a prayer in religious science is
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.73,0:42:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that you have what's called the realization stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.73,0:42:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,where you affirm or claim that this good
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.73,0:42:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming to this person's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.73,0:42:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That good is coming to this person's life?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.76,0:42:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the particular good that they mention.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.76,0:42:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, their particular good, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.76,0:42:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and it brings me into a lot of conflict
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.76,0:42:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,because I've heard you say, and, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.76,0:42:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the absolute truth, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.76,0:42:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't want to interfere in someone's karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.76,0:42:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can't anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.76,0:42:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and so, right, and, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.76,0:42:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't want to try because then, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.76,0:42:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember you answered a question
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.76,0:42:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,about a lady whose sister was alcoholic,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.76,0:42:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and you said, you know, you're just,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.76,0:42:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,every time you rescue her, you're pushing her further away.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.76,0:42:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And so all of this has come to play
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.76,0:42:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in my attempts to pray for people
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.76,0:42:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,who come and ask me to pray for some particular good,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.76,0:42:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.76,0:43:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but you're seeing yourself as a doer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.76,0:43:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.76,0:43:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a doer, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.76,0:43:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only a presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.76,0:43:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So the presence plus your intention
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.76,0:43:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is all that you can do as a prayer,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.76,0:43:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,as the prayer person.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.76,0:43:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And the acceptance of that, the fulfillment of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.76,0:43:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,depends on their personal karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.76,0:43:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to override it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.76,0:43:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not like you're overriding a person's personal karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.76,0:43:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.76,0:43:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So you pray, dear Lord, for a healing
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.76,0:43:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to the degree that it can be done
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.76,0:43:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,by that divine grace and mercy, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.76,0:43:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and now it's up to divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.04,0:43:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's a little bit different from
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.49,0:43:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,what we are told, from how we're told to pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.49,0:43:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, say it again, how you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.49,0:43:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We just affirm that this particular good
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.49,0:43:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming to this person's life,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.49,0:43:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,like if they want a really good job or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.49,0:43:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, it's okay, it's optimism.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.49,0:43:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.49,0:43:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So we affirm that this person here present,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.49,0:43:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,about whom we are praying,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.52,0:43:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,will be coming into the needed job
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.52,0:44:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to support his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.52,0:44:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Right? Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.52,0:44:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Something, yeah, something like that, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.52,0:44:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.52,0:44:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to violate their karma,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.52,0:44:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,because if...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.52,0:44:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.52,0:44:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The very fact that they've asked you to pray for them
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.52,0:44:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,has already changed their karma, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.52,0:44:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.65,0:44:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.65,0:44:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.65,0:44:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The very fact that they've asked God's help,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.65,0:44:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're just an avenue with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.65,0:44:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a vehicle, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.65,0:44:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.65,0:44:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're just an avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.65,0:44:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still up to divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.65,0:44:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and propensity of proclivity
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.74,0:44:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,of manifesting an actuality out of a potentiality,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.74,0:44:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,which you're just one of the agents in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.66,0:44:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.66,0:44:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And we do think of ourselves as vehicles,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.66,0:44:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet I want to pray accordingly,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.66,0:44:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, according to God's grace and so forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.66,0:44:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's just,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.66,0:44:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not something that you say in a religious science prayer,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.66,0:44:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.66,0:44:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it verboten?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.66,0:44:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, do they excommunicate you or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.66,0:45:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it in accordance with God's will?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.66,0:45:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I never got that out of religious science,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.66,0:45:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's that restrictive.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.66,0:45:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think it would be verboten.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.66,0:45:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.66,0:45:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm having trouble finding the correct wording.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.66,0:45:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think that's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.66,0:45:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.66,0:45:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're uncertain how to contextualize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.66,0:45:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.66,0:45:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just add,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.66,0:45:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,in accordance with thy will, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.66,0:45:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And in accordance with the highest good, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.24,0:45:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.24,0:45:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I see a Mercury coming into your future,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.24,0:45:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,a Ford,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.24,0:45:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,all in accordance with God's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.24,0:45:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A new SUV.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.24,0:45:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.24,0:45:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.24,0:45:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.24,0:45:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is just the way you were contextualizing it
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.24,0:45:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,you were worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.24,0:45:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.24,0:45:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we did a sermon at a workshop at religious science
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.43,0:45:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,about a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.43,0:45:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, we've always asked for a Mercedes Benz.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.78,0:45:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.78,0:45:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We've always asked for a Mercedes Benz.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.78,0:45:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.01,0:45:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And a Mercedes Benz, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.19,0:46:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Mercedes Benz.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.19,0:46:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, it's my understanding that it's more spiritually advantageous
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.19,0:46:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to see the ego as a friend rather than an adversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.19,0:46:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've become quite concerned lately
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.19,0:46:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,about the behavior of my friend, the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.19,0:46:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The friend who?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.19,0:46:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,His friend, ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.19,0:46:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He's become concerned about the behavior of his friend, ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.19,0:46:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.19,0:46:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you were in the depths of the pits of hell with the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.19,0:46:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and finally he let go,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.19,0:46:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,was the ego capable of learning anything from that experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.48,0:46:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.48,0:46:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.48,0:46:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Got frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.48,0:46:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.48,0:46:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.48,0:46:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.48,0:46:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.48,0:46:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.48,0:46:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.48,0:46:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.67,0:46:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.91,0:46:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.91,0:46:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.91,0:46:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.91,0:46:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.91,0:46:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.91,0:47:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, flames are the upper part of hell, that's just the frosting on the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.03,0:47:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawking?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.03,0:47:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.29,0:47:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you got to get it over here and into the mic.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.29,0:47:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.29,0:47:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How does one cultivate love so it's not objectified?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.29,0:47:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a capacity, a way of being, in the appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.26,0:47:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that all of creation is the unfolding of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.26,0:47:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Evolution is the unfolding of divinity, of the unmanifest becoming manifest and discernible via linearity.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.53,0:47:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So your consciousness is like a probe from the non-linear into the linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.62,0:47:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.25,0:47:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The incredible beauty of the flowers, you see, is God.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.16,0:48:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's saying you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.44,0:48:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.04,0:48:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this microphone correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.67,0:48:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.71,0:48:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.65,0:48:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,See, as you evolve, the incredible beauty of everything begins to shine forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.86,0:48:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In the beginning, you only see it in that which is blatantly aesthetically pleasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.84,0:48:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,As it goes on, you begin to see it in everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.21,0:48:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that everything is perfect and everything is incredibly beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.17,0:48:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If we had enough time, I'd tell you about it, but anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.75,0:48:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to ask you if you would ohm.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.09,0:48:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants you to do an ohm.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.37,0:48:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nico did an ohm.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.32,0:48:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants you to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.27,0:48:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want me to do an ohm?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.97,0:49:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you do a good ohm.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.13,0:49:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You ohmed in my son's face, and he said his knees buckled, and so I thought, well, I want that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.15,0:49:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I did an ohm.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.79,0:49:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.91,0:49:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, when he met you previously.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.37,0:49:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.17,0:49:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.33,0:49:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You better get crazy soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.93,0:49:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep telling me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.87,0:49:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to just.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.51,0:49:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're going to flip out.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.35,0:50:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect to get ohm today, by golly.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.72,0:50:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a different lifetime where I did ohm.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.18,0:50:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, we all did ohm together.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.68,0:50:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Caught amongst through eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.87,0:50:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.62,0:50:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.48,0:50:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.90,0:50:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you give us some more understanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.54,0:50:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Of how to release accumulated negative karma?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.86,0:50:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.66,0:50:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How to release an accumulated negative karma?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.16,0:50:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the undoing of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.68,0:50:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The undoing of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.72,0:50:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's the purpose of this lifetime, undo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.04,0:50:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're presented with the same thing you didn't forgive before, and now this time you've got the option to forgive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.61,0:50:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's like a representation of opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.28,0:51:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So by striving, you gain good karma, you might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.76,0:51:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are presented with limitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.00,0:51:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So the constant letting go of the limitation, negative feelings and perceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.88,0:51:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a continuous process.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.28,0:51:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can describe it as a contemplative way of being in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.38,0:51:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life becomes the prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.56,0:51:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the supplication to divinity by the quality of your presentation to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.08,0:51:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.87,0:51:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.89,0:51:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.29,0:51:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is you be this.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.58,0:51:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you don't have to do anything, verbalize anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.00,0:51:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the prayer by virtue of the alignment and contextualization of your existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.60,0:51:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.91,0:52:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life becomes a supplication and an invocation.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.89,0:52:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life becomes the prayer of invocation by which your existence is constantly reflecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.50,0:52:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The divinity and will of God as it's comprehensible to this level of consciousness now.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.38,0:52:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about it because you are it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.78,0:52:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you describe the relationship between mind and consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.54,0:52:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, mind generally means mentation, mentalization, intellectualization, visualization, ideas, memories, you know, consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.29,0:52:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ask me about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.49,0:52:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.99,0:52:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness is the underlying field which itself is non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.41,0:53:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the light by which you see the linearity of the thinkingness, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.66,0:53:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that you're thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.27,0:53:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know you're thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.93,0:53:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,By being aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.91,0:53:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.15,0:53:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,By becoming aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.53,0:53:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How come you're aware?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.61,0:53:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does awareness come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.15,0:53:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.57,0:53:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You woke up with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.13,0:53:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You came into this life with consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.15,0:53:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.41,0:53:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The consciousness is not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.09,0:53:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a quality you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.35,0:53:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.47,0:53:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's protoplasmic.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.77,0:53:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't create protoplasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.56,0:53:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You are, you know, you came into this life with protoplasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.74,0:53:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The capacity to be aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.03,0:53:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So I say, you know, as a contemplative lifestyle or a meditative style, you would draw from
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.99,0:53:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,identification with the movie and the linearity.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.61,0:53:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You move into the awareness of self as the witness observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.55,0:53:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The witness observer witnesses all the time, watches.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.79,0:53:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't get involved or participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.97,0:53:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.87,0:54:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't think about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.19,0:54:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It witnesses it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.13,0:54:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.87,0:54:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a spectator.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.01,0:54:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So as you move out of participating in the movie to the witness of the movie, then you're
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.87,0:54:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the watcher of the witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.55,0:54:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you say, the watcher of the witness, where do they come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.26,0:54:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They come from awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.62,0:54:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Awareness comes from consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.32,0:54:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness comes from divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.02,0:54:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nonlinear.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.98,0:54:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.16,0:54:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.90,0:54:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,As you move your identification out of the out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.42,0:54:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Out there-ness, you'll see that what is innate is an impersonal quality that's independent
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.99,0:54:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.69,0:54:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's getting closer and closer to the self as consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.14,0:54:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So how could consciousness by error choose oneness or singleness?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.97,0:54:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, how can consciousness error?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.17,0:54:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you said it in chapter 18 of this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.59,0:54:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How can consciousness error?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.39,0:54:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.73,0:54:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You said.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.71,0:55:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness can.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.31,0:55:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,By error, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.09,0:55:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You said by error can.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.95,0:55:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I got the word right?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.45,0:55:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.67,0:55:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe I'm saying it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.02,0:55:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The error occurs within consciousness itself before there is even any person involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.74,0:55:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness can experience itself either as singularity or as oneness.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.36,0:55:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.88,0:55:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That is mine to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.64,0:55:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.24,0:55:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't quite understand your question.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.20,0:55:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the chapter 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.99,0:55:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.81,0:55:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.55,0:55:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How do spiritual errors come about?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.04,0:55:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a pretty general question.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.62,0:55:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It would have taken an hour to answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.12,0:55:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How do spiritual errors come about?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.96,0:55:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really asking the nature of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.36,0:55:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the a priori quality out of which awareness arises?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.95,0:55:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.91,0:55:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the background feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.25,0:56:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the background field out of which awareness then becomes progressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.76,0:56:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It expresses to the witness, the observer, and then the witnesser, the observer of the linear what, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.63,0:56:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But independent of what, what, is the innate nonlinear quality of consciousness itself, which prevails all the time, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.53,0:56:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You all see?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.06,0:56:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I say, look past the content.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.82,0:56:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Underneath the mind is an infinite field of stillness.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.19,0:56:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You can focus on that any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.07,0:56:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to go into a meditative state.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.37,0:56:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Be aware that it's like the ocean, and the thoughts are like the fish flying out.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.66,0:56:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.88,0:56:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus on that which, what is the condition just before the thinkingness arises?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.44,0:56:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not linear sequentially, but the substrate of all thinkingness, out of which all thinkingness arises, is an infinite field always available.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.15,0:57:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you are, the infinite field of consciousness, which is, which is vacant of content.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.53,0:57:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like space.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.03,0:57:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Space exists independent of whether there's anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.57,0:57:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything in it or not is going to drive me crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.71,0:57:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He's 22.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.33,0:57:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.05,0:57:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.17,0:57:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.17,0:57:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll move along faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.15,0:57:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We got a good one coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.91,0:57:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.55,0:57:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.18,0:57:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, all.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.34,0:57:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to thank you all for being supportive, and in this group, I have gained a lot of strength and courage facing my situation right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.96,0:57:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is, I'd like to seek advice on how to deal with my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.78,0:57:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.14,0:57:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart has been beating very nervously, very fast, in the past year and a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.87,0:57:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And it gets intensified when I'm exposed to spiritual teachings, spiritual teachers, and spiritual groups like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.13,0:57:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Like when I read the book, I, in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.91,0:58:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it better or worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.17,0:58:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.07,0:58:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.81,0:58:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Very exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.95,0:58:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.63,0:58:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost like overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.85,0:58:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.43,0:58:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yeah, I like to, like, I try different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.74,0:58:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I try to argue.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.52,0:58:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, puncture.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.90,0:58:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.64,0:58:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.22,0:58:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.64,0:58:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, my heart is no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.26,0:58:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Paroxysmal tachycardia?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.58,0:58:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he call it?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.05,0:58:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Paroxysmal tachycardia?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.75,0:58:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he suggest a beta blocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.44,0:58:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A beta blocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.58,0:58:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that cuts down overreaction to adrenaline?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.31,0:58:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.67,0:58:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't suggest a beta blocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.02,0:58:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ordinarily, a beta blocker would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.66,0:58:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, everything that's physical, mental, and spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.84,0:58:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you want to block off the symptom itself, but at the same time, you also want to see the origin of it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.02,0:58:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.52,0:58:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just emotional excitement as you get closer and closer to spiritual truth, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.52,0:58:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.02,0:58:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what would.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.44,0:58:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachycardia.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.44,0:58:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He needs a beta blocker, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.44,0:58:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.44,0:58:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.44,0:58:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I would try a simple beta blocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.44,0:59:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They're very cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.44,0:59:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Generic.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.44,0:59:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Beta blocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.44,0:59:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Beta blocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.44,0:59:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They call.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.44,0:59:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you write it down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.44,0:59:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.54,0:59:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Midoprolol.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.54,0:59:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Midoprolol.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.54,0:59:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to prescribe as a physician now, but you should ask your doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.54,0:59:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.64,0:59:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.64,0:59:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I go to him, then he listen to my heart, and then he beats normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.64,0:59:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.64,0:59:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.64,0:59:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,When I visit the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.64,0:59:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,When he sees the doctor, it's beating normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.64,0:59:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.64,0:59:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.64,0:59:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,See, he doesn't have to see the tachycardia.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.64,0:59:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You just tell him, you know, I have periodic periods of tachycardia, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.64,0:59:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need a tranquilizer for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.64,0:59:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need the tranquilizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.64,0:59:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A beta blocker decreases sensitivity to adrenaline.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.64,0:59:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You may react to excitement over adrenaline.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.64,0:59:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.64,0:59:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.64,0:59:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.64,0:59:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, is it going to be a transition thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.08,0:59:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can just take it for a while, and then I.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.08,0:59:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.08,0:59:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.08,0:59:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.08,0:59:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just symptomatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.08,0:59:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.08,0:59:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.08,0:59:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.08,0:59:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.08,0:59:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.08,0:59:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.08,0:59:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.08,0:59:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.08,0:59:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.08,0:59:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm going to take it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.08,0:59:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take it very low dose.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.08,0:59:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.08,0:59:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.08,0:59:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, that's.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.08,0:59:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,See, everything's physical, mental, and spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.08,0:59:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.08,0:59:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's the physical, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.08,0:59:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the mental, I don't know, the excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.66,1:00:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And the emotional, I'm not sure about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.72,1:00:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that would take some period of investigation.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.74,1:00:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't have probably reached it just in a question and answer period.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.82,1:00:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.82,1:00:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A related question is, when I go to, like, crowded places, like to subway in big cities.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.14,1:00:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.14,1:00:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I feel I share the emotions of the people.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.14,1:00:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.14,1:00:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And they kind of worsen my organs.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.08,1:00:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.08,1:00:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, my heart sometimes feel beating very fast, my stomach tight, or I feel agony, loneliness,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.08,1:00:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,emptiness.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.08,1:00:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.08,1:00:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.08,1:00:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.08,1:00:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you need to just continue working on a spiritual level, and you'll transcend all
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.08,1:00:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.37,1:00:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, beta blockers are very cheap.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.37,1:00:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I shouldn't ask you that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.37,1:00:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the temporary.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.37,1:00:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The physical, the mental, and the spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.37,1:00:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.37,1:00:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.37,1:00:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the Course in Miracles says the physical, the mental, and the spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.05,1:00:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the physical is only the expression of the intention of the spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.37,1:00:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.37,1:00:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,People think, you know, if I pray for a job, it's going to come out of the sky.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.37,1:00:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember a guy said, I prayed and prayed for a job, and nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.44,1:01:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it hadn't been for my brother-in-law calling me up, I'd still be unemployed.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.29,1:01:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.29,1:01:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,God didn't answer his prayer for a job, and his brother-in-law saved him.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.28,1:01:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't see the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.28,1:01:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.28,1:01:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.28,1:01:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.28,1:01:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.34,1:01:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.34,1:01:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Beta blockers are cheap.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.34,1:01:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They're pretty safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.34,1:01:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm talking about temporary relief, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.34,1:01:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Long-term, you'll transcend this whole level of anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.34,1:01:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is a medical question.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.56,1:01:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If the calibration level of a physician can influence the outcome of a treatment, does
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.56,1:01:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the calibration level of the patient also influence?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.56,1:01:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.56,1:01:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.56,1:01:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got an interaction of two energy fields.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.56,1:01:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.56,1:01:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.56,1:01:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, being a physician, a lot of times I can't control the calibration level of
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.56,1:01:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the patient.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.56,1:01:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.56,1:01:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But the calibration level is reflecting their karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.56,1:01:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So they may be karmically entitled to a recovery, or they may not.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.69,1:02:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And your field may or not, you know, you can't impose your will on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.88,1:02:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do your intention, you do your physical.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.88,1:02:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I suggest you're on the physical, mental, and spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.01,1:02:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So I tell them, physically this is what I do, mentally this is what I do, and spiritually
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.01,1:02:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,this is what I advise.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.59,1:02:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's up to them, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.87,1:02:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I think all things are physical, mental, and spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.87,1:02:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.22,1:02:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a beta blocker and also go to the Course of Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.22,1:02:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Also go to the Course of Miracles and see a good psychotherapist.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.22,1:02:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're doing it at an all-terrain level.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.22,1:02:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this authentic here?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.22,1:02:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that funny?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.22,1:02:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything else?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.22,1:02:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.22,1:02:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to sign this?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.22,1:02:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
