Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.38,1:19:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond the animal kingdom because it's seeking to
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.36,1:19:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,return to its source.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.28,1:19:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.43,1:19:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you want to do is avoid any
