Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.15,1:19:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,how creation
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.11,1:19:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,appears to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.77,1:19:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Because let's say
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.09,1:19:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,by calibrating, there's an inference
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.03,1:19:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that one thing is better than another.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.73,1:19:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really better.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.98,1:19:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Each thing can become the perfection
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.10,1:19:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,of its own level.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.04,1:19:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The perfect amoeba is the perfect amoeba
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.16,1:19:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that's already fulfilled
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.30,1:19:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,perfection within its own domain.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.06,1:19:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Yeah. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.20,1:19:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.44,1:19:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Boone Gordon from Silverthorne, Colorado
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.60,1:19:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and a World War II fighter pilot.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.66,1:19:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I came back from the war
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.12,1:19:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and I noticed
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.46,1:19:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that there was a sense of community
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.66,1:19:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that we had in our fighter squadron.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.96,1:20:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I also noticed there wasn't
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.64,1:20:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,this purpose we had in the war.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.02,1:20:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And I also noticed that
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.22,1:20:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,there wasn't much spirituality.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.62,1:20:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When we were fighter pilots, we seemed to
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.52,1:20:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,tap into the source.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.12,1:20:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, so about 1950
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.16,1:20:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I started meditating
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.66,1:20:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,with Raja Yoga.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.06,1:20:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And I started getting these messages
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.90,1:20:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,on how to design a town of the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.00,1:20:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And so
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.22,1:20:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,now these ideas are mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.00,1:20:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So they're on this book here for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.30,1:20:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't that nice?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.36,1:20:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And the question is
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.26,1:20:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that most of the
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.40,1:20:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,ideas are above 500 consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.90,1:20:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I call it LQ.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.30,1:20:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, light quotient.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.44,1:20:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And now my question is,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.28,1:20:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,how can I get this word out?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.62,1:20:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And how can I find the people
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.68,1:20:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,for this town of the future?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.14,1:20:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Any suggestions?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.76,1:20:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.44,1:20:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to put out a call.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.24,1:20:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, this is putting out a call right here
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.00,1:20:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,for people to join you in this quest.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.62,1:20:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And the quest is what?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.66,1:20:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,To establish sort of a heavenly state
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.40,1:21:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,here on Earth or in other dimensions?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.73,1:21:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we want to build an actual city
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.69,1:21:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,because then people will look and see
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.13,1:21:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that this higher consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.57,1:21:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a city of light.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.25,1:21:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A city of light.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.13,1:21:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,On the physical realm?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.63,1:21:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a physical realm.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.35,1:21:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're too old for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.08,1:21:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that 1,200 of us
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.16,1:21:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,are dying each day in World War II.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.12,1:21:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think I have a couple years left.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.28,1:21:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think a city of light
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.78,1:21:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,would take, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.71,1:21:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,something more than a few years.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.40,1:21:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.49,1:21:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think if you hold it in mind,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.35,1:21:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,then that tends to manifest.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.75,1:21:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can certainly join with artists
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.51,1:21:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,to hold it in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.59,1:21:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But the practicality of how to manifest it
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.97,1:21:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,in the linear domain,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.09,1:21:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.03,1:21:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.37,1:21:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a lot of money?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.09,1:21:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't have any money.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.89,1:21:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need money.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.69,1:21:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it all figured out.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.77,1:21:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.39,1:21:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, the vision would...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.59,1:21:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, I think I know what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.69,1:21:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I already got what you said.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.15,1:21:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got the whole design
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.33,1:22:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that you have in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.43,1:22:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.05,1:22:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying it's not doable.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.97,1:22:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But what you're questioning
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.11,1:22:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,is really how to present it
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.25,1:22:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and create an attraction to the idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.85,1:22:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.27,1:22:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.23,1:22:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How to promulgate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.91,1:22:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.53,1:22:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.79,1:22:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Other than writing a book,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.65,1:22:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,about it,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.39,1:22:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,or talking on the radio,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.93,1:22:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,or I don't know how else.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.02,1:22:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.03,1:22:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's adorable.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.49,1:22:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.19,1:22:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, my name is Vishali Shaheen.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.73,1:22:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from Oakland, California.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.97,1:22:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.51,1:22:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.31,1:22:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,about two years ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.57,1:22:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I liquidated all my assets
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.09,1:22:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to pay off my debt
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.47,1:22:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and save some money
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.23,1:22:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and moved in with friends
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.31,1:22:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and living very quietly.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.59,1:22:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And after a few years of that,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.93,1:22:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.33,1:22:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on a spiritual path,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.49,1:22:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I just kind of went,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.57,1:22:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,wow, it would be nice
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.29,1:22:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to have more in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.83,1:22:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A relationship, a home,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.91,1:22:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,things like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.39,1:22:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,As I'm getting older.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.09,1:22:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And the question is,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.95,1:22:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.97,1:23:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in wanting a better life,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.22,1:23:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to create more karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.08,1:23:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.30,1:23:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're always going to create karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.92,1:23:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe good karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.41,1:23:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with just living a normal life?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.71,1:23:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that would be.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.65,1:23:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, we don't see
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.67,1:23:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,how I'm living a normal life.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.33,1:23:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm living with friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.47,1:23:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.17,1:23:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But a normal life to me
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.21,1:23:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,would be a home,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.21,1:23:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,a relationship.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.93,1:23:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so how do you bring that
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.09,1:23:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,into manifestation?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.93,1:23:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you're asking?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.39,1:23:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm going to,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.31,1:23:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to bring that
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.23,1:23:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,into manifestation.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.07,1:23:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess my intention
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.05,1:23:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is to make sure that I
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.35,1:23:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,do that in a way
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.41,1:23:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that doesn't create more karma
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.77,1:23:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,because I would like
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.67,1:23:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to continue evolving
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.39,1:23:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,on this path
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.01,1:23:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,without being distracted
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.93,1:23:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,by worldly stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.43,1:23:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But having it,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.41,1:23:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,opening up to God's abundance
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.65,1:23:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and allowing that to be
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.25,1:23:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and not creating more karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.81,1:23:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, can you accomplish
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.41,1:23:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,some worldly goal
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.93,1:23:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,without creating more karma?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.23,1:23:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.64,1:23:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.62,1:23:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.65,1:24:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,okay,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.65,1:24:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,it's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.65,1:24:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You see,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.07,1:24:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,you hold in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.39,1:24:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you value.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.65,1:24:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what you hold in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.73,1:24:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically manifests,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.39,1:24:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,not as a doingness,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.47,1:24:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,not as a this and a that
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.53,1:24:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,which creates karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.81,1:24:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You hold in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.05,1:24:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,a vision for yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.09,1:24:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,because that which you hold in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.57,1:24:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,tends to manifest.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.11,1:24:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's up to divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.15,1:24:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to fulfill it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.81,1:24:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The divinity of the karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.96,1:24:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.71,1:24:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayor?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.47,1:24:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.41,1:24:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.90,1:24:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What you hold in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.24,1:24:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,tends to manifest.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.14,1:24:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We calibrated that
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.04,1:24:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.38,1:24:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hold it in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.24,1:24:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,without volition,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.14,1:24:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,without trying to make it happen
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.28,1:24:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,or force it
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.98,1:24:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,or cause it or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.28,1:24:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.02,1:24:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.02,1:24:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about yoga
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.88,1:24:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and qigong.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.58,1:24:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was seeing
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.10,1:24:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in your new book,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.16,1:24:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,which of course
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.90,1:24:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't read,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.36,1:24:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was looking
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.18,1:24:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,at somebody else's book.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.14,1:24:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And hatha yoga
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.22,1:25:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and qigong,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.06,1:25:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget exactly,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.16,1:25:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.54,1:25:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,they both calibrate
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.68,1:25:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,240, 260.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.54,1:25:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, positive.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.48,1:25:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.18,1:25:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, but I wanted to know
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.24,1:25:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,what's wrong with them.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.72,1:25:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.16,1:25:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing wrong with them.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.92,1:25:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you're over 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.12,1:25:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you mean
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.64,1:25:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,what's wrong with them?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.28,1:25:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.06,1:25:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha didn't say
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.98,1:25:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to do that to get enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.24,1:25:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So I mean,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.56,1:25:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,do you expect it to be 800 or what?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.16,1:25:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.80,1:25:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.36,1:25:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the reason I asked
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.66,1:25:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,is that I love,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.70,1:25:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I teach those things.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.98,1:25:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.22,1:25:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And I love teaching them.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.88,1:25:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wanted to make sure
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.88,1:25:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that I wasn't teaching
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.06,1:25:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,something false.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.94,1:25:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.36,1:25:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They're very integrous.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.10,1:25:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.42,1:25:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, but I mean,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.02,1:25:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,if you compare that
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.10,1:25:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to like modern medical science,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.94,1:25:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,which is at 400,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.08,1:25:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.52,1:25:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,well, why shouldn't I just tell
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.82,1:25:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,all my yoga students
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.64,1:25:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,just go to the doctor?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.24,1:25:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't make sense to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.34,1:25:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't go to a doctor
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.26,1:25:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,for spiritual advancement,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.92,1:25:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.30,1:25:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it didn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.44,1:25:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're trying to apply
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.40,1:25:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,apples and peaches.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.52,1:25:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They're two different realms,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.46,1:25:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.02,1:25:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, what she's doing
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.12,1:25:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is she's saying that
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.06,1:26:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,240 is lower than 400.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.88,1:26:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.42,1:26:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're comparing
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.16,1:26:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,of apples and pears
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.66,1:26:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're two different things.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.76,1:26:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.28,1:26:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, going to the Louvre,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.68,1:26:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, there's pictures
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.54,1:26:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Louvre that are 700.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.98,1:26:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you shouldn't be doing
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.92,1:26:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.56,1:26:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be sending
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.06,1:26:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,all these people to the Louvre.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.34,1:26:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Send everybody to the Louvre
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.82,1:26:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and give up whatever you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.32,1:26:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.32,1:26:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, so, but.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.22,1:26:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that's important
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.02,1:26:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,is what you're doing
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.70,1:26:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is over 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.64,1:26:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.38,1:26:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.54,1:26:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.28,1:26:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it matter
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.78,1:26:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that I love what I'm doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.42,1:26:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.38,1:26:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.62,1:26:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.14,1:26:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.50,1:26:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you're only asking
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.00,1:26:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,about a mechanical technique.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.64,1:26:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not asking about
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.58,1:26:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the intention of the practitioner,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.06,1:26:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,which is probably
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.70,1:26:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,far more powerful
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.54,1:26:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,than the technique.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.76,1:26:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.26,1:26:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of your intention
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.26,1:26:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and your love for your patients,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.14,1:26:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, they're going to do fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.16,1:26:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.92,1:26:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, somebody who calibrates
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.04,1:26:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to 180 and is doing these things
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.62,1:26:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,just for the money,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.40,1:26:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, maybe their people
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.28,1:26:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,don't get better, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.44,1:26:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.14,1:26:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.62,1:26:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So the most important thing
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.88,1:27:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,is my intention as a practitioner.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.66,1:27:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.38,1:27:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.68,1:27:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the technique.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.36,1:27:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the technique
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.04,1:27:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,is just the mechanism,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.82,1:27:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the means, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.72,1:27:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.52,1:27:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.40,1:27:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.34,1:27:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.36,1:27:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is there anything wrong
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.34,1:27:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,with yoga or qigong?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.72,1:27:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to make sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.36,1:27:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.40,1:27:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.86,1:27:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.34,1:27:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They're okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.50,1:27:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They're integrous.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.46,1:27:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They're above 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.30,1:27:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They're integrous.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.12,1:27:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in line with truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.60,1:27:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.30,1:27:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.22,1:27:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.76,1:27:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They're healing techniques.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.00,1:27:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.44,1:27:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.68,1:27:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, look at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.51,1:27:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She's integrous.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.49,1:27:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she asked.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.89,1:27:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to just verify
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.97,1:27:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the integrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.61,1:27:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She did it because
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.59,1:27:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,there's so many bogus things
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.67,1:27:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,out there, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.65,1:27:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And she just wants to make sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.69,1:27:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.16,1:27:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen many times
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.16,1:27:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you perform kinesiological testing
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.98,1:27:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,with Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.54,1:27:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know in power versus force,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.38,1:27:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you describe a technique
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.00,1:27:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can perform
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.98,1:28:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,on your own.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.74,1:28:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you go to that again?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.38,1:28:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.56,1:28:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't find it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.40,1:28:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've looked at the book all over.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.78,1:28:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She should demonstrate.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.16,1:28:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you demonstrate
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.10,1:28:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the self?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.90,1:28:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to know
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.86,1:28:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,kinesiology testing
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.26,1:28:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,like the self.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.76,1:28:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the ring finger.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.72,1:28:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.20,1:28:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.30,1:28:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people can do it themselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.28,1:28:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I say kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.12,1:28:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is like riding a bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.44,1:28:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people are gifted
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.14,1:28:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to get it right away.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.96,1:28:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Other people struggle
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.70,1:28:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and keep falling off the bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.60,1:28:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You hold Abraham Lincoln.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.12,1:28:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You hold these two fingers
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.22,1:28:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.26,1:28:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, use this like a hook.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.34,1:28:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.68,1:28:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm holding Abraham Lincoln
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.84,1:28:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.72,1:28:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.17,1:28:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,well, that's saying it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.65,1:28:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying anything
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.85,1:28:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,about Abraham Lincoln.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.85,1:28:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just holding Abraham Lincoln
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.99,1:28:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,in my mind, you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.78,1:28:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what I'm doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.73,1:28:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thumb and third finger.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.35,1:28:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.85,1:28:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I use this.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.59,1:28:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I make a hook out of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.73,1:28:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.68,1:28:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.24,1:28:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I hold these together
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.70,1:28:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,strongly.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.51,1:28:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.01,1:28:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm holding Abraham Lincoln
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.51,1:28:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.03,1:28:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and I try to break the ring.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.63,1:28:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.23,1:28:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.27,1:28:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.70,1:28:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.04,1:29:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.44,1:29:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.32,1:29:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.60,1:29:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.22,1:29:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.46,1:29:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.74,1:29:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hold.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.46,1:29:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.86,1:29:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.10,1:29:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.16,1:29:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.22,1:29:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.24,1:29:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.26,1:29:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.28,1:29:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.34,1:29:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.40,1:29:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.42,1:29:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.48,1:29:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.58,1:29:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.60,1:29:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.64,1:29:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.82,1:29:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop laughing.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.54,1:29:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold Ben Loudman in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.58,1:29:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture Ben Loudman.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.70,1:29:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,His staff and all that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.98,1:29:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.62,1:29:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.46,1:29:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, pull your fingers apart again.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.16,1:29:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You see any difference in the strength?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.94,1:29:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, not the tip of your finger,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.50,1:29:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but actually higher up, I noticed.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.84,1:29:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.90,1:29:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.70,1:29:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.50,1:29:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to make something
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.64,1:29:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,very simple and complicated.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.02,1:29:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You just go like this
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.98,1:29:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and you go like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.28,1:29:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.64,1:29:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.98,1:29:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.12,1:29:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to go to college for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.48,1:29:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.14,1:29:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have to be right.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.02,1:29:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The best thing to do
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.14,1:29:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is it isn't a test of strength.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.16,1:29:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.94,1:29:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.34,1:29:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a test of relative strength.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.86,1:29:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What it is is you see,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.28,1:29:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,when you feel,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.88,1:29:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,you get the feel of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.78,1:29:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.02,1:29:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you put it in
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.92,1:29:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and you say,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.08,1:29:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,okay, Ben Loudman.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.38,1:29:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.88,1:29:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.18,1:29:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's another way of doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.40,1:29:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You take something
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.10,1:29:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that weighs a couple pounds
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.20,1:29:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,like a brick.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.88,1:29:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.64,1:29:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.30,1:29:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold this up in front of you
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.62,1:29:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,about the chest height.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.82,1:29:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a new way
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.32,1:29:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm showing everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.94,1:29:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.58,1:29:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.84,1:30:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hold Abraham Lincoln in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.14,1:30:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and now lift this.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.60,1:30:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.05,1:30:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.55,1:30:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,hold Ben Loudman in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.27,1:30:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and try and lift it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.24,1:30:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It weighs a great deal more
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.54,1:30:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,when I hold Ben Loudman
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.66,1:30:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have much more difficulty
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.94,1:30:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,lifting it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.49,1:30:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.09,1:30:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I just came across recently.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.71,1:30:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't really tested it out
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.83,1:30:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm not recommending it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.37,1:30:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.57,1:30:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you heard it here.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.57,1:30:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was trying to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.71,1:30:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I do it all by myself?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.29,1:30:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,See,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.57,1:30:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,other than this technique
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.51,1:30:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think somebody said it there
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.29,1:30:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.95,1:30:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.67,1:30:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you lift a certain weight
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.87,1:30:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,holding one thing in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.93,1:30:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and then lift the same weight
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.09,1:30:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,holding something else in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.19,1:30:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And just compare the amount
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.57,1:30:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,of strength it takes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.17,1:30:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And I found I could do kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.65,1:30:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,on my own
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.29,1:30:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,even when she's doing something else
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.83,1:30:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,out in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.49,1:30:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Practice makes perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.37,1:30:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a comparison
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.63,1:30:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,of the relative ease.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.59,1:30:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.63,1:30:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes a lot of effort
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.69,1:30:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to lift these bricks
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.63,1:30:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,when I hold him in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.41,1:30:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and when I hold him in line
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.81,1:31:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems to go easier.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.43,1:31:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.31,1:31:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.27,1:31:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.97,1:31:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,about pendulum work?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.16,1:31:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.98,1:31:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it's useful.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.76,1:31:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I would not use it
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.86,1:31:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in the negatives.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.54,1:31:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't check out
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.38,1:31:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the universe
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.48,1:31:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of the lower astral
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.38,1:31:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,with a pendulum.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.78,1:31:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're inviting like lightning
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.10,1:31:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to hit your rod.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.38,1:31:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.82,1:31:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We were going to do
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.82,1:31:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,a healing prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.34,1:31:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We were going to do
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.38,1:31:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,a healing prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.64,1:31:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of people here
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.04,1:31:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,for healings
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.92,1:31:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and could we do
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.68,1:31:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,a healing prayer?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.24,1:31:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what that is.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.34,1:31:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.28,1:31:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.83,1:31:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.96,1:31:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of body again.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.50,1:31:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.02,1:31:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.83,1:32:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the healing prayer?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.53,1:32:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.56,1:32:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.36,1:32:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,it's my joy
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.74,1:32:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to be with you
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.48,1:32:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,as usual
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.06,1:32:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and we look forward
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.34,1:32:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to the next time.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.76,1:32:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,As I say,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.48,1:32:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we're evolving
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.04,1:32:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,into a very,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.78,1:32:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,very powerful group.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.88,1:32:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Very powerful group.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.80,1:32:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Group intention
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.40,1:32:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,of a people this advanced
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.70,1:32:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,impacts the universe.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.05,1:32:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It lifts the overall field
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.13,1:32:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.71,1:32:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,of all of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.97,1:32:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It benefits everyone
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.09,1:32:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,not on a causal,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.23,1:32:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,not on a causal,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.43,1:32:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,of this causing of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.47,1:32:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,As a consequence
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.27,1:32:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which we have become
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.65,1:32:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to align yourself,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.11,1:32:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,surrender yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.71,1:32:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to divinity,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.02,1:32:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,fulfill your karmic
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.10,1:32:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,potentiality to the fullest,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.88,1:32:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,what more can you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.12,1:32:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.79,1:32:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to live
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.53,1:32:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,in such a way
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.35,1:32:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,that your life is a prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.35,1:32:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to live
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.91,1:32:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,your life in such a way
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.07,1:32:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that you have no
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.55,1:32:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,anxiety at all
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.32,1:32:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,about meeting God.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.71,1:32:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you willing
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.27,1:32:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to be answerable
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.27,1:32:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,for who you are
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.35,1:32:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and what you've done
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.71,1:32:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,with what you are?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.59,1:33:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What more can you ask?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.83,1:33:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What more can you ask?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.31,1:33:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That I live in such a way
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.71,1:33:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that frankly,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.31,1:33:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.29,1:33:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of talking to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.43,1:33:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done the damnedest I can
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.99,1:33:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,in every direction here.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.49,1:33:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I've pushed myself
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.35,1:33:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to the limit
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.85,1:33:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to be the fulfillment
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.59,1:33:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,of my potential.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.38,1:33:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That relieves me
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.14,1:33:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,of all guilt
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.76,1:33:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,because now I can make
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.84,1:33:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.92,1:33:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I make a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.89,1:33:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the overall context,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.61,1:33:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you see,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.33,1:33:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've sanctified
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.82,1:33:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.10,1:33:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,By your overall intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.20,1:33:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, by intention,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.98,1:33:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,then,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.78,1:33:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,our life becomes
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.14,1:33:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the devotion.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.56,1:33:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We become the prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.64,1:33:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,By virtue of that,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.78,1:33:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we invoke divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.94,1:33:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And then through the heart,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.38,1:33:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,through the heart,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.14,1:33:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,through the devotion,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.01,1:33:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,through the alignment
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.73,1:33:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,with divinity,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.80,1:33:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we empower all of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.84,1:33:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.14,1:33:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.32,1:34:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,we say,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.12,1:34:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Gloria in excelsis,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.24,1:34:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Deo.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.87,1:34:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Glory
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.29,1:34:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to God
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.17,1:34:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,in the highest.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.00,1:34:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And what more
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.72,1:34:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,could be said?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.41,1:34:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.91,1:34:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,how far in the room?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.17,1:34:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.41,1:34:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you like it,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.71,1:34:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll spend more and more time
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.85,1:34:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,with individual questions
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.03,1:34:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and answers
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.57,1:34:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll leave it up
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.39,1:34:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to the group.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.02,1:34:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.36,1:34:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it up to the group.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.61,1:34:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it now.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.99,1:34:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Would people favor
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.91,1:34:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,more time
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.79,1:34:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,with personal questions
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.91,1:34:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and answers
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.49,1:34:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and spontaneous interviews?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.07,1:34:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.79,1:34:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Vis-a-vis didactic teaching.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.21,1:34:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see the answer for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.83,1:35:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we've got a lot of scholars here, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.09,1:35:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.47,1:35:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, well, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.37,1:35:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,we make it half and half
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.33,1:35:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,because we're always discovering new things
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.15,1:35:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.53,1:35:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,we want to present it on every level
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.09,1:35:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,from the heart
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.79,1:35:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and from the intellect,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.83,1:35:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,from the mind, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.53,1:35:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And we,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.29,1:35:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason doesn't,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.69,1:35:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't just stuck in 400
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.01,1:35:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,because you see reason
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.01,1:35:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,in and of itself
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.65,1:35:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates in the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.41,1:35:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you use reason
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.89,1:35:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,as a means
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.27,1:35:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.89,1:35:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,pursuing,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.35,1:35:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,pursuing God,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.53,1:35:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,pursuing spiritual intention,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.37,1:35:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,then you've sanctified the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.61,1:35:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.81,1:35:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not just using it
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.21,1:35:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,for its own egoistic.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.93,1:35:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.59,1:35:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you can sanctify
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.71,1:35:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,your intellect
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.89,1:35:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and you say,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.37,1:35:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,for the old Lord,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.59,1:35:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.09,1:35:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,do I try to understand
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.17,1:35:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and incorporate these teachings
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.53,1:35:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that they may bring me closer
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.01,1:35:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,to the old Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.07,1:35:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you can sanctify
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.97,1:35:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the mind
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.05,1:35:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,essentially.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.75,1:35:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.47,1:35:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is different than a secular mind
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.11,1:35:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,which is only looking for
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.37,1:36:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to squeeze
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.21,1:36:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the gain out of information.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.65,1:36:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.69,1:36:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.99,1:36:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,let's,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.43,1:36:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,how's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.01,1:36:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll sanctify the mind collectively.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.10,1:36:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Lord,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.58,1:36:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,we do surrender our collective minds
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.56,1:36:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to thy service
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.96,1:36:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that we may
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.12,1:36:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,be
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.26,1:36:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the fulfillment
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.72,1:36:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of thy potential
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.88,1:36:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,in this demand,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.88,1:36:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,in this dimension.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.38,1:36:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.82,1:36:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to be an intellectual.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.84,1:36:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.11,1:36:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, golly.
